quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  27,64,"Kapena Iye amene poyambirira adapanga zolengedwa ndiponso amene adzatidzutsanso kukhala ndi moyo m’moyo umene uli nkudza ndiponso amene amakupatsani chakudya kuchokera ku nthaka ndi kumwamba? Kodi pali mulungu winanso woonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni? Nena, “Tionetseni chizindikiro chanu ngati zimene mukunenazi ndi zoonadi.”"
  27,65,"Nena, “Palibe amene ali kumwamba kapena pa dziko lapansi amene amadziwa zobisika kupatula Mulungu. Ndiponso anthu sadziwa nthawi imene adzaukitsidwa kukhalanso ndi moyo.”"
  27,66,Kodi kuzindikira kwawo m’moyo umene uli nkudza kwakwaniritsidwa? Iwo ndi okaika pa zamoyo umene uli nkudza ndipo maso awo ndi otsekeka pa za iwo
  27,67,"Anthu osakhulupirira adati, “Kodi pamene ife ndi makolo anthu, tisanduka dothi tidzaukitsidwanso?”"
  27,68,“Ndithudi ife tidalonjezedwa ndiponso makolo athu. Ichi si china ayi koma nkhani zopanda pake za anthu akale.”
  27,69,"Nena, “Pitani pa dziko lonse lapansi ndipo mukaone zimene zidawaonekera anthu ochimwa.”"
  27,70,Usachite chisoni kapena kuvutika mu mtima chifukwa cha ziwembu zimene apanga
  27,71,"Ndipo iwo amati, “Kodi lonjezo limeneli lidzakwaniritsidwa liti ngati zimene muli kunenazi ndi zoona?”"
  27,72,"Nena, “Mwina gawo lina la zimene muli kufuna kuti zidze msanga zili pafupi kudza.”"
  27,73,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ambuye wako ndi wokoma mtima kwa anthu, koma ambiri a iwo sathokoza ayi"
  27,74,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ambuye wako amadziwa zonse zimene zimabisika m’mitima mwawo ndiponso zonse zimene amaulula"
  27,75,Kulibe chinsinsi kumwamba kapena padziko lapansi chimene sichidalembedwe mu Buku lake lolemekezeka
  27,76,Buku la Korani lili kuwauza ana a Israyeli zambiri zimene iwo amatsutsana